Class DictionaryBuilder

java.lang.Object
org.example.DictionaryBuilder
public class DictionaryBuilder extends Object
DictionaryBuilder– manages the hash table, implements methods: DictionaryBuilder(int estimatedEntries)- Constructor that creates a hash table appropriate for the estimated entries. Must consider load factor and 4k+3 prime table size. DictionaryBuilder(String filename)- Constructor that reads a file and adds all the words to the DictionaryBuilder Methods: 1/ addWord(String word) 2/ getCount(String word) 3/ removeWord(String word) 4/ getAllWords()– return sorted ArrayList of all the words in the dictionary
